
---

## `.gitignore`

```gitignore
# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini

# Editors / IDE
.vscode/
.idea/
*.code-workspace

# Node (if you add a build step later)
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*
*.map

# Composer (if you add PHP deps later)
vendor/
composer.lock

# WordPress local env
.wp-env.json
wp-env/
wordpress/
wp-content/uploads/

# Env & secrets
.env
.env.*

# Builds / archives
dist/
build/
*.zip
*.tar
*.tar.gz

# Tests / coverage
coverage/
.phpunit.result.cache
.phpunit.cache/
tests/artifacts/
phpunit.xml
phpunit.xml.dist

# Logs
*.log
